2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a new training strategy for improving classification accuracy using machine learning techniques. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep learning classifiers for the task of lymph node diagnosis, which falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MS (Medical Imaging): The paper deals with the analysis of medical images (abdominal CT scans) for the purpose of diagnosing metastatic lymph nodes. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the analysis of multimedia data (CT scans) for the purpose of medical diagnosis.
